text: The Spell is the second studio album by the Swiss progressive metal band Cellar Darling. It was released on 3 March 2019 by Nuclear Blast. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== ===Musicians=== * Anna Murphy – vocals, hurdy-gurdy, flute, keyboard * Ivo Henzi – guitars, bass guitar * Merlin Sutter – drums ==Charts== {|class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" style="text- align:center;" |- !scope="col"|Chart (2019) !scope="col"|Peak position |- |- |} ==References== Category:2019 albums Category:Cellar Darling albums Category:Nuclear Blast albums Category:Death in music
